   "text": "W1  replay a fixture twice \u2192 identical event-ID sets \u00b7 cargo test green with no gRPC key      [~done]\nW2  kill -9 mid-batch \u2192 restart \u2192 verify reports ZERO missing, ZERO duplicate                  [next]\nW3  gap self-heals under verify \u00b7 12h soak clean \u00b7 Grafana from one command                    [later]\nW4  benchmark 1x/5x/10x documented \u00b7 demo video \u00b7 a stranger says 'this person ships infra'   [later]",
