   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 216670578,
   "versionNonce": 1065627487,
   "text": "capture (Stage 4)  \u2192  golden tests today  \u00b7  fixture mode for reviewers with no paid key (W2)  \u00b7  crash-test input (W2)  \u00b7  benchmark input (W4)\nThis is why Stage 4 came before Stage 6, even though storing data felt more exciting. Foundation before downstream \u2014 always.",
   "fontSize": 12.5,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
